This was changed when switching to `SafeMustacheFactory` in https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/92211 which sets [`allowChangingDelimeters`](https://github.com/spullara/mustache.java/blob/c17bb110161848e444576e93170a2a696770e9d3/compiler/src/main/java/com/github/mustachejava/SafeMustacheFactory.java#L82) to `false`.
